data.description: Discover the charm of this delightful rancher. This home features three generously sized bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, providing comfort and style in every corner. Step into the living room and enjoy the natural light that shines through the large bay window. The laminate flooring throughout, lends a glossy finish to the open kitchen adorned with granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances. Nestled beside the kitchen is a sunroom/family room that beckons you to unwind by the fireplace while overlooking the backyard. Enjoy entertaining friends and family in the partially finished basement, complete with a convenient wet bar. This additional living space adds versatility to the home, making it perfect for game nights, parties, or a cozy movie evening. In the summer you can enjoy entertaining or relaxing in the fenced in back yard which includes a large patio and deck. This home is conveniently located with easy access to major highways to make commuting a breeze. Schedule your showing today!
